  "reference_number": "RUS2035",
  "remarks": "\nAvioChem is an involved person under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 because AvioChem is or has been involved in destabilising Ukraine or undermining or threatening the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine, by making available goods or technology that could contribute to destabilising Ukraine or undermining or threatening the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine, and is obtaining a benefit from or supporting the Government of Russia by operating in a sector of strategic significance to the Government of Russia, namely the Russian Transport sector.\n",
